        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>filmmaking and filmmaking processes and techniques [300263875], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Collectively, all the processes and techniques employed in the creation of motion pictures on film or videotape, including directing, performing, producing, filming, editing, writing and design. Specifically refers to the activities of film or video directors and producers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Colectivamente, todos los procesos y técnicas empleados en la creación de las películas o la videocinta, incluyendo dirección, la ejecución, produción, editar, escribir y diseño. Refiere específicamente a las actividades de la película o los directores y los productores de vídeo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In het algemeen: alle processen en technieken die worden gebruikt bij het maken van rolprenten op film of videoband, waaronder regie, acteerwerk, productie, opnemen, montage, script en ontwerp. Verwijst met name naar de werkzaamheden van film- of videoregisseurs en -producenten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>廣泛地指稱為了在膠捲或是錄影帶上創造出動態影像所運用之過程與技術，包含了導演、表演、製作、攝影、剪接、編劇以及設計。特別是指稱電影或錄影導演與製作人所進行的各項活動。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
